Dame Joan, 89, shared her joy at welcoming her youngest, and 15th, godchild yesterday, as she shared a sweet family photo. She typed: “With my youngest #godchild yet, the son of my oldest #godson @adambricusse. “Now I have 15 #godchildren and I love them all,” she added. Joan looked chic in the snap as she wore her hair in an elegant up-do. She kept her makeup simple with a slick of mascara and her signature red lipstick, while fans marvelled over how youthful the Dynasty actress looked.